flowchart TD
    Start([User Request])

    Start --> Choice{Workflow Type?}

    %% Prototype Workflow Branch
    Choice -->|New Project| P1[Natural Language<br/>Description]
    P1 --> P2[prepare_prototype_context]
    P2 --> P3{Parse Success?}
    P3 -->|No| P4[Return Error<br/>with Suggestions]
    P3 -->|Yes| P5[Structured Context<br/>product, platform, screens]

    %% MCP Workflow Branch
    Choice -->|Existing Project| M1[Load Project Context]
    M1 --> M2{Context Exists?}
    M2 -->|No| M3[Return Error<br/>Create context first]
    M2 -->|Yes| M4[Project State Loaded<br/>features, routes, components]
    M4 --> M5[Feature Request<br/>+ Context]
    M5 --> M6[plan_increment]
    M6 --> M7[Increment Plan<br/>scope, references, patterns]

    %% Convergence Point
    P5 --> Gen[generate_prototype]
    M7 --> Gen

    Gen --> V0[Send to v0 API]
    V0 --> Stream{Streaming?}
    Stream -->|Yes| Progress[Stream Progress<br/>Updates]
    Stream -->|No| Direct[Direct Response]
    Progress --> Proto[Prototype Result]
    Direct --> Proto

    Proto --> Check{Success?}
    Check -->|No| Error[Return Error<br/>with Details]
    Check -->|Yes| Result[Screens + Components<br/>+ Preview URL]

    Result --> Handoff[handoff_to_claude_dev]
    Handoff --> Brief[Implementation Brief<br/>UX patterns, rules]

    Brief --> Impl{Workflow Type?}

    %% Prototype Workflow End
    Impl -->|Prototype| PEnd([Ready for<br/>Implementation])

    %% MCP Workflow Continue
    Impl -->|MCP| Dev[Claude Dev<br/>Implements Feature]
    Dev --> Update[update_project_context]
    Update --> Save[Save to<br/>project-context.json]
    Save --> MEnd([Ready for<br/>Next Feature])

    %% Error Handling
    P4 --> End1([End])
    M3 --> End2([End])
    Error --> End3([End])

    style Start fill:#4A90E2
    style PEnd fill:#50C878
    style MEnd fill:#50C878
    style Error fill:#FF6B6B
    style P4 fill:#FF6B6B
    style M3 fill:#FF6B6B
